Invocation Name: doggy tags
des:
Doggy Tags skill is for folks wanting ideas about new, often amusing, descriptive, and sometimes whimsical doggy names.

Doggy names can often be a glimpse into the interests, diversions, and psyche of dog owners. Doggy names express emotion, elicit response, and celebrate infinite canine personalities. Names can cause people to judge a dog and react positively or negatively when meeting it.

So enjoy Doggy Tags for fun and entertainment. Or use it for the serious task of deciding what to call your "Best Friend", that "Lovable Mutt", the one who inspires you to be the person he or she thinks you are. And even better....

Let’s make Doggy Tags even better! For every FIVE, 5 Star reviews this skill gets in the Alexa app, the developer promises to upgrade the skill with one hundred(100) new doggy names. So, by leaving a 5 star review you tell the developer it’s worth putting more time and effort into development. Costs you nothing, and inspires further development... an easy win-win, right? Each new upgrade will give Doggy Tags a fresh "Leash on Life".

And you'll find this especially "Fetching"! - When we get to TWENTY FIVE, 5 star reviews we'll upgrade the skill with "Ask for Doggy Tags Alphabetically" so you can easily hear names by the first letter.

So that's how you can easily do your part to help improve and continue development of this skill... cool, right? Now, time to "Howl" and "Raise the Woof"... This is so much fun, my tail's waggin'!
